  "detailed_description": "Join Ellen in her quest to complete an internship for the Witch Academy and find out what happened in her supervisor's Manor! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198270/extras/61635d5252c002d8a5c96d730f0ace75.poster.avif?t=1609063592\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198270/extras/61635d5252c002d8a5c96d730f0ace75.webm?t=1609063592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198270/extras/61635d5252c002d8a5c96d730f0ace75.mp4?t=1609063592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198270/extras/beca371a53bc91474fac90bfebe664e9.apng?t=1609063592\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198270/extras/beca371a53bc91474fac90bfebe664e9.poster.avif?t=1609063592\" class=\"bb_img\" width=384 height=124 /></picture></span><br><br>An adventure game with lots of puzzles, a retro feeling, interactive magic and a talking squirrel ghostl!<br>- Many different types of <strong>puzzles</strong>: from escape-rooms to riddles and item combination!<br>- <strong>Magic system</strong>: spells that interact with the enviroment, such as the \"Magnet Spell\" to move metal objects and the \"Light Spell\" to light up small fires or turn on lights! Unlock more as you progress with the story!<br>- A lively cast of <strong>crazy characters with original design and personality</strong>!<br>- <strong>Plot full of mystery</strong> with secrets and multiple endings!<br>- Original <strong>artwork</strong> by artist Caterina Capogrossi. <br><br>Inspired by classic point-and-click adventure games and with a cartoon look that's just too cute to resist, \"The Button Witch\" is an original and polished game for all ages! Don't forget to bring your magic wand!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198270/extras/120f9e9c2df0a347fc170bed9f982014.poster.avif?t=1609063592\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198270/extras/120f9e9c2df0a347fc170bed9f982014.webm?t=1609063592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198270/extras/120f9e9c2df0a347fc170bed9f982014.mp4?t=1609063592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can also find \"The Button Witch\" bundled with the Digital Soundtrack:<br><br>And the Artbook and Guide:<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198270/extras/4b93f60d3a96875b7b7e0162f24785fa.webp?t=1609063592\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198270/extras/4b93f60d3a96875b7b7e0162f24785fa.poster.avif?t=1609063592\" class=\"bb_img\" width=384 height=121 /></picture></span>",
